sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant X as Apex<br/>(Anonymous / Queueable)
    participant N as Named Credential<br/>Engine (Salesforce)
    participant T as Auth0 Token Endpoint<br/>your-tenant.us.auth0.com/oauth/token
    participant M as Auth0 Management API<br/>/api/v2/users

    X->>N: callout:Auth0_Mgmt_API/api/v2/users
    Note over N: No valid token cached?<br/>Get one first — automatically.
    N->>T: POST grant_type=client_credentials<br/>client_id + client_secret (from Principal)<br/>+ audience (Custom Request Parameter)
    T-->>N: 200 OK — access_token (Bearer)
    N->>M: POST /api/v2/users (create)<br/>GET /api/v2/users/{id} (read)<br/>PATCH /api/v2/users/{id} (update)<br/>DELETE /api/v2/users/{id} (delete)
    M-->>N: 2xx + JSON
    N-->>X: HttpResponse

    Note over X,M: Full CRUD with one setup —<br/>the token dance never appears in your code
